                               c0-7.3-6-13.3-13.3-13.3s-13.3,6-13.3,13.3v225.1c0,7.3,6,13.3,13.3,13.3h133c7,0,12.7-5.4,13.3-12.3c0-0.3,0.1-0.7,0.1-1V342
